<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV73">
<l>marampotac caranturantu vālivīḻa muṉṉornā</l>
<l>ḷurampotacca ranturanta vumparāḷi yempirāṉ</l>
<l>varaṅkuṟippil vaittavarkka lātuvāṉa māḷilum</l>
<l>nirampunīṭu pōkametti ṟattatumyārkku millaiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Except for the people whom Our Lord, the Ruler of the celestials</l>
<l>—who shot on a previous day an arrow so that Vālin fell [and his] chest</l>
<l rend="indent">was perforated, having shot an arrow so that the trees were perforated—</l>
<l>placed in [His] excellent thoughts,</l>
<l>the full, permanent enjoyment is in no way for anyone, even if [they] rule over the sky!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
